data.description: This remarkable home, available at an exceptional price, boasts a picturesque curb appeal highlighted by an inviting front porch. Inside, updated flooring, fresh paint, abundant natural light, and a spacious kitchen with ample cabinet space create a welcoming atmosphere. With three bedrooms, two baths, and a one-car garage, this residence is poised for new ownership, offering a perfect blend of comfort and entertainment potential with its expansive backyard.
